title: Morphine - Black sessions no. 51 (rare live performance)
description:
This is a recording of a live show of Morphine called the black sessions, which is a performance for a French radio show. it was recorded April 6, 1994 at Le Melody, Brest france.
It is supposed to be a rare recording limited to 2500 pieces.
more information www.blacksessions.tk
